<section class="section-spacing section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      <!-- Card 1: Bajas y Tasacion -->
      <div class="group bg-light rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 border border-grey-200 shadow-sm hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary-700 group-hover:bg-primary-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-dark">Bajas y Tasacion de Vehiculos</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-grey-600">Gestion integral con la DGT</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-grey-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Compramos su vehiculo al mejor precio. Gestionamos la baja definitiva ante la DGT
          y le proporcionamos el certificado oficial. Recogemos el coche en toda la comarca sin coste.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span>Tasacion maxima por su vehiculo</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span>Grua gratuita en Ejea y comarca</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span>Certificado de baja DGT inmediato</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a href="/baja-vehiculo" class="btn-primary">
          Tramitar Baja
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Recambios -->
      <div class="group bg-light rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 border border-grey-200 shadow-sm hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary-700 group-hover:bg-primary-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-dark">Piezas de Coche de Desguace</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-grey-600">Recambios revisados con garantia</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-grey-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Miles de recambios de segunda mano a precios inmejorables. Todas las piezas estan revisadas
          y cuentan con garantia. Enviamos a toda Espana en 24/48 horas.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span>Garantia en todas las piezas</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span>Envio a toda Espana</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span>Calidad revisada pieza a pieza</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a href="/recambios" class="btn-primary">
          Ver Recambios
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
